snippet.textDisplay: The songs that come from this Coke Studio are incredible with voices of Monali and Shilpa..   the musicians are the most outstanding!  Take time to listen to this Season 2 ,  they are amazing ,, this album and Ravi and Anoushka,  carried me through Cancer Treatments in 2016, 2017..   I played flute but the cancer took my abilities all away..,  after 40+ of years playing last 15 for pure joy.  I always wanted to play Bansuri … on my next trip around ,  I will learn.l. Thank you gifted musicians and voices !
